PrecisAuthority to enter into the CANADA-NOVA SCOTIA OFFSHORE TAX ADMINISTRATION AGREEMENT whereby the Province, as Agent of Her Majesty, will collect and administer the consumption taxes and insurance premium taxes imposed in the offshore area under sections 212 and 213 of this Act.

precis:
Authority to enter into the CANADA-NOVA SCOTIA OFFSHORE TAX ADMINISTRATION
AGREEMENT whereby the Province, as Agent of Her Majesty, will collect and
administer the consumption taxes and insurance premium taxes imposed in
the offshore area under sections 212 and 213 of this Act.
